{"tid":481975,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[求問]外國邊間學府讀漢學研究master 好？","createTime":"2017-11-27T16:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T07:43:23.000Z","uid":71040,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1743ade4ab3eee706dfc32d4ff33b5ffeda5f7a2","tid":481975,"uid":71040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:50:33.000Z","msg":"今年4月讀完BA，宜家一邊做教畜，一邊讀緊local MA。規律生活過得多，發現始終有個留學夢，想去歐美留學，趁後生冇重擔，有能力就想快完夢，唔想一世都營營役役。<br />\n<br />\n本來諗過儲下錢(窮L家庭)，以後去外國讀PhD，不過計落條數要付出太大，風險太高。後來諗深一層，發覺自己最想都只係去歐美體驗下生活，同拎張名聲不錯學府嘅砂紙，所以計落，讀master比較實際，適合自己多啲。<br />\n<br />\n(以前讀書時都有去過Exchange ，但中文系都只係去過北大，冇機會去外國。)<br />\n<br />\n咁既然讀書，根據自己嘅底同興趣，發覺讀漢學、東亞語言文化類學科，會啱自己興趣多啲。問題就嚟啦，雖然唔想做伸手黨，但始終識嘅太少，都想問吓熟悉嘅巴打意見，邊度讀漢學或者相關學科比較好？<br />\n<br />\n有睇過少少資料，暫時見到倫敦大學亞非學院嘅課程幾出名，都啱自己（MA Chinese Studies/Sinology/Sinology (Literature Pathway))，<br />\n<br />\n咁美國東岸 ivy league 好似太勁有距離感，又唔多熟，都冇乜點睇。西岸 UCLA（Chinese Language and Culture/ Cultural and Comparative Studies &ndash; China Focus）或者UC berkeley（Asian Studies）暫時覺得值得一試。<br />\n<br />\n當然，由於全部都係名校，都好有機會報考唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但始終係自己想做嘅事，點都想一試，求熟悉嘅巴打比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9abb8062e011756b95896aeda0774ff9e8a103f1","tid":481975,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:06:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔使讀pgde 都可以教書？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 唐人去西洋學漢學感覺好怪"},{"pid":"14a395355df18ff793e63392afd8d531a523bf77","tid":481975,"uid":71040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T17:14:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔使讀pgde 都可以教書？<br />\n<br />\nbtw 唐人去西洋學漢學感覺好怪</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能好彩掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，我都係上網搵再寄信apply，佢肯請就得，但之後要補返Pgde<br />\n<br />\n去外國讀漢學，主要係開下眼界，用西方世界嘅角度去睇中國社會同文化。文化係比較之下更有價值，或者發掘到傳統一家之學見唔到嘅盲點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4955d28c93e9e56ebc40a698020640d62cdeea2c","tid":481975,"uid":153362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T20:21:57.000Z","msg":"有fd係W&uuml;rzburg讀漢學,仲可以去北大exchange<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sinologie.uni-wuerzburg.de/studienangebot/master-chinese-studies/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sinologie.uni-wuerzburg.de%2Fstudienangebot%2Fmaster-chinese-studies%2F&d=kyY9N8uN2swg7R%2BSD1S4n5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=47058375\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sinologie.uni-wuerzburg.de/studienangebot/master-chinese-studies/</a>"},{"pid":"fe9d2ce0d353866b325fce333829d725e47c339f","tid":481975,"uid":71040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T23:07:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有fd係W&uuml;rzburg讀漢學,仲可以去北大exchange<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.sinologie.uni-wuerzburg.de/studienangebot/master-chinese-studies/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sinologie.uni-wuerzburg.de%2Fstudienangebot%2Fmaster-chinese-studies%2F&d=kyY9N8uN2swg7R%2BSD1S4n5UJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=47058375\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.sinologie.uni-wuerzburg.de/studienangebot/master-chinese-studies/</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae149ca2a9d7825dcc4c16073c66551f5208c22b","tid":481975,"uid":154554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"西岸唔考慮埋Stanford?"},{"pid":"abdaf83b348f61df4557f7fb5d3322d1ec5eefe1","tid":481975,"uid":71040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T06:40:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>西岸唔考慮埋Stanford?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇咗下，見佢有開East Asian Languages and Cultures<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cla